# Byrokratt MCP server integration

At **the start of EACH chat**, load the rules for the module of the file you are editing. You can use the `byrokratt-mcp` MCP server to load the rules. The module names in the MCP server match the repository folder names exactly (e.g., `Service-Module`, `Training-Module`, `Analytics-Module`, `Buerokratt-Chatbot`, `Chat-Widget`).
